观察¶

  1. cap-shape: =b=c=x=f=k=s
  2. cap-surface: =f=g=y=s
  3. cap-color: =n=b=c=g=r=p=u=e=w=y
  4. bruises: =t=f
  5. odor: =a=1=c=y=f=m=n=p=s
  6. gill-attachment: =a=d=f=n
  7. gill-spacing: =c=w=d
  8. gill-size: =b=n
  9. gill-color: =k=n=b=h=g=r=o=p=u=e=w=y
  10. stalk-shape: =e=t
  11. stalk-root: -=b=c=u=e=z=r=
  12. stalk-surface-above-ring: =f=y=k=s
  13. stalk-surface-below-ring: =f=y=k=s
  14. stalk-color-above-ring: =nBUff=b=c=g=o=p=e=w=y
  15. stalk-color-below-ring: =n=b=c=g=o=p=e=w=y
  16. veil-type: =p=u
  17. veil-color: =n=o=w=y
  18. ring-number: 0=n1=o2=t
  19. ring-type: cobwebby=c=eflling=f=lnone=n=p=szone=z
  20. spore-print-color: =k=n=b=h=r=o=u=w=y
  21. population: =a=c=n=s=v=y
  22. habitat: =g=1=m=p=u=w=d

3. 初步探索¶

  • K-means
  • k
In [12]:
import time
from sklearn.metrics import silhouette_score
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
In [13]:
def cluster(X):
    '''
    K-Means
    
    
        X
    
        best_clusters
        score
        
    '''
    print('{}'.format(len(X.columns)))
    score = -1
    duration = 0
    start = time.time()
    
    # K215
    clusters_num = range(2, 15)
    
    for cluster in clusters_num:  
        # kmeanscluster
        kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=cluster, random_state=0)
        
        # kmeansXXtest_preds
        test_preds = kmeans.fit_predict(X)

        # silhouette_scoretest_score
        test_score = silhouette_score(X, test_preds)
        
        # 
        print("k = {}, component score is {}".format(cluster, test_score))

        #
        if (score < test_score):
            best_clustersnum = cluster
            score = test_score
            best_clusters = kmeans

    # 
    end = time.time()      
    duration += end - start

    # 
    print(': {:.4f}s'.format(duration))
    print('k{}{:.3f}'.format(best_clustersnum, score))
    
    return best_clusters, score
